安德烈·根纳季耶维奇·卡尔洛夫1954年出生于莫斯科，毕业于[[莫斯科国立国际关系学院|莫斯科国立国际关系学院]]国际经济关系学系。他于1976年在[[苏联外交部|苏联外交部]]开始了他的职业生涯。苏联解体后，卡尔洛夫继续在{{Link-ru|俄羅斯駐朝鮮大使館|Посольство России в КНДР}}担任各种外交职务。一直到2013年7月，卡尔洛夫改调俄罗斯驻土耳其大使馆担任大使。<ref>{{cite news|title=Who was Andrey Karlov? What we know about the Russian ambassador to Turkey|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/12/19/andrey-karlov-know-russian-ambassador-turkey/|work=The Telegraph|access-date=2016-12-19|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220133730/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/12/19/andrey-karlov-know-russian-ambassador-turkey/|dead-url=no}}</ref>卡尔洛夫是继[[亚历山大·格里伯耶多夫|亚历山大·格里伯耶多夫]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://lenta.ru/articles/2016/12/20/killed_ambassador|title=Четвертый на посту: посол России в Турции Андрей Карлов|last=|first=|date=2016-12-20|work=Lenta.ru|trans-title=Fourth in the line of duty: Russian Ambassador Andrei Karlov killed in Turkey|access-date=2016-12-20|via=|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019055547/https://lenta.ru/articles/2016/12/20/killed_ambassador/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{le|瓦茨拉夫·沃罗维斯基|Vatslav Vorovsky}}和前苏联驻波兰大使{{le|皮约托·沃伊科夫|Pyotr Voykov}}后，第四位在任期间殉职的俄罗斯大使<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bromwich|first1=Jonah Engel|title=Who Was Andrey Karlov, the Russian Ambassador Killed in Turkey?|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/19/world/europe/andrey-karlov-wiki.html|accessdate=2016-12-20|work=The New York Times|date=2016-12-19|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309035536/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/19/world/europe/andrey-karlov-wiki.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

