凶徒梅尔鲁特·莫特·奥尔塔廷斯（{{IPA-tr|ˈmevlyt ˈmæɾt ˈɑɫtɯntɑʃ|lang}}；1994年6月24日-2016年12月19日）是事发时休班的警察，生于土耳其西北部爱琴海地区[[艾登省|艾登省]][[瑟凯|瑟凯]]城的[[世俗|世俗]]家庭。尽管瑟凯城是土耳其最古老的城镇之一，但在奥尔塔廷斯家人居住的周围，[[民族主义|民族主义]]和[[伊斯兰主义|伊斯兰主义]]十分盛行。诸如“上帝应该给予土耳其人”和“伊斯兰是唯一的道路”等口号是该地区常见的涂鸦<ref name="Reuters 23 Dec">{{cite news|last1=Gumrukcu|first1=Tuvan|title=Russian envoy's killer remembered as lonely boy, not angry jihadist|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-russia-diplomat-assailant-idUSKBN14C1FM|work=Reuters|date=2016-12-23|accessdate=2016-12-24|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108143638/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-russia-diplomat-assailant-idUSKBN14C1FM|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他自从2所大学將之劝退后<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-russia-diplomat-assailant-idUSKBN14C1FM|title=El Gumrukcu, Tuvan (23 December 2016).|website=Reuters|access-date=2016-12-24|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108143638/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-russia-diplomat-assailant-idUSKBN14C1FM|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，2014年从伊兹密尔警察学校毕业<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaceta.es/noticias/asesino-andrei-karlov-policia-turco-22-anos-19122016-1943|title=El asesino de Andrei Karlov, un policía turco de 22 años|date=2016-12-19|website=La Gaceta|accessdate=2016-12-19|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002212536/https://gaceta.es/noticias/asesino-andrei-karlov-policia-turco-22-anos-19122016-1943|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。他在安卡拉的防爆警察部队服役了2年半。直到2016年7月，他曾有8次参加土耳其总统埃尔多安的安保工作<ref name="telegraph">{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/12/21/russian-ambassadors-assassin-guarded-recep-tayyip-erdogan/|title=Russian ambassador's assassin 'guarded Recep Tayyip Erdogan'|date=2016-12-21|website=The Telegraph|accessdate=2016-12-24|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108195804/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/12/21/russian-ambassadors-assassin-guarded-recep-tayyip-erdogan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

土耳其媒体报道称，奥尔塔廷斯牵涉[[2016年土耳其政变|政变]]，于10月停职，但于11月中旬复职<ref>{{cite news|title=Karlov's assassin stayed in hotel close to scene, took 11 shots|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/karlovs-assassin-stayed-in-hotel-close-to-scene-took-11-shots.aspx?PageID=238&NID=107528&NewsCatID=509|accessdate=2016-12-20|publisher=Hürriyet Daily News|date=2016-12-20|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019060855/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/karlovs-assassin-stayed-in-hotel-close-to-scene-took-11-shots.aspx?PageID=238&NID=107528&NewsCatID=509|dead-url=no}}</ref>。土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安认定奥尔塔廷斯是安卡拉防暴警察的一员<ref name="ABCNews20Dec">{{cite news|title=Who was the Ankara assassin?|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-12-20/ankara-russian-ambassador-shooting-who-is-mevlut-mert-aydintas/8135510|work=ABC News|date=2016-12-20|language=en-AU}}</ref>。

== 各方反应 ==
[[File:Putin,_Lavrov,_Bortnikov,_Naryshkin_(2016-12-19).jpg|thumb]]
许多[[国家元首|国家元首]]纷纷谴责此次袭击，同时向大使家属及其他受害者和俄罗斯人民表示慰问。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mzv.cz/jnp/en/issues_and_press/mfa_statements/x2016_12_19_mfa_of_the_czech_republic_condemns_the.html|title=Statement of the MFA of the Czech Republic on the Assassination of Russian Ambassador to Turkey|date=2016-12-19|website=[[捷克共和国外交部|捷克共和国外交部]]|accessdate=2016-12-19|archive-date=2017-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170115123731/http://www.mzv.cz/jnp/en/issues_and_press/mfa_statements/x2016_12_19_mfa_of_the_czech_republic_condemns_the.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.state.gov/secretary/remarks/2016/12/265774.htm|title=The Assassination of Russian Ambassador to Turkey Andrey Karlov|newspaper=U.S. Department of State|access-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220020255/http://www.state.gov/secretary/remarks/2016/12/265774.htm|archive-date=2016-12-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 

尽管[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]并未声称对袭击负责，但它的支持者们已经开始庆祝<ref >{{cite news|title=ISIS ‘Celebrates’ Assassination of Russian Ambassador to Turkey Andrei Karlov|url=http://heavy.com/news/2016/12/isis-islamic-state-tahwid-allahu-akbar-assassination-attempt-russian-ambassador-to-turkey-andrei-karlov-twitter-video-claim/|work=Heavy.com|date=2016-12-19|accessdate=2016-12-22|archive-date=2017-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170805153352/http://heavy.com/news/2016/12/isis-islamic-state-tahwid-allahu-akbar-assassination-attempt-russian-ambassador-to-turkey-andrei-karlov-twitter-video-claim/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据埃及报纸《{{le|第七日|Youm 7}}》的报道，包括[[征服沙姆阵线|征服沙姆阵线]]在内的伊斯兰教[[征服者|征服者]]联盟声称对暗杀事件负责<ref >{{cite news|title=ISIS ‘Celebrates’ Assassination of Russian Ambassador to Turkey Andrei Karlov|url=http://tass.com/world/921186|work=[[俄通社-塔斯社|俄通社-塔斯社]]|date=2016-12-21|accessdate=2016-12-25|archive-date=2018-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724062815/http://tass.com/world/921186|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

卡塔尔记者伊尔哈姆·巴达尔（{{lang|en|Elham Badar}}）表示枪击案是对俄罗斯在阿勒坡及其他冲突地区的野蛮反应的个人回应<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/qatari-journalist-russian-ambassador-shooting-dead-deserved-syria-crimes-air-strikes-andrei-karlov-a7486321.html|title=Qatari journalist posts: Russia ‘deserved’ ambassador killing for its ‘crimes’ in Syria|work=The Independent|accessdate=2016-12-21|archive-date=2016-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222011433/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/qatari-journalist-russian-ambassador-shooting-dead-deserved-syria-crimes-air-strikes-andrei-karlov-a7486321.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。《[[纽约每日新闻|纽约每日新闻]]》专栏作家格什·昆特玆曼（{{lang|en|Gersh Kuntzman}}）將卡尔洛夫遇害案和犹太学生{{le|赫佐尔·格林斯潘|Herschel Grynszpan}}刺杀纳粹德国外交官{{le|恩斯特·冯·莱特|Ernst vom Rath}}的事件進行比較，表示“正义得到彰显”，引来舆论批评<ref>{{cite web|last1=Gersh|first1=Kuntzman|title=Assassination of Russian Ambassador Andrei Karlov was not terrorism, but retribution for Vladimir Putin’s war crimes|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/don-cry-russia-slain-envoy-putin-lackey-article-1.2917281|website=New York Daily News|accessdate=2016-12-20|archive-date=2017-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112052811/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/don-cry-russia-slain-envoy-putin-lackey-article-1.2917281|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Pfeiffer|first1=Alex|title=NY Daily News Columnist Defends Assassination Of Russian Ambassador|url=http://dailycaller.com/2016/12/20/ny-daily-news-columnist-defends-assassination-of-russian-ambassador/|accessdate=2016-12-23|archive-date=2017-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112092828/http://dailycaller.com/2016/12/20/ny-daily-news-columnist-defends-assassination-of-russian-ambassador/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[俄罗斯外交部|俄罗斯外交部]]其后要求《纽约每日新闻》刊文道歉<ref>{{cite web|title=Russian Foreign Ministry demands apology from NY Daily News – spokesperson|url=https://www.rt.com/news/371187-russia-us-daily-apology/|publisher=RT|accessdate=2016-12-23|archive-date=2016-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224031400/https://www.rt.com/news/371187-russia-us-daily-apology/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。因[[乌克兰亲欧盟示威运动|亲欧盟示威运动]]讲话闻名的前乌克兰内政部长{{le|沃洛迪马伊·帕拉斯乌基|Volodymyr Parasiuk}}称刺客是英雄<ref>{{cite web|title=Ukrainian MP calls Russian ambassador’s killer ‘a hero,’ FB reacts with outrage|url=https://www.rt.com/news/371006-unkraine-reaction-russian-ambassador/|publisher=RT|accessdate=2016-12-20|archive-date=2019-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812093549/https://www.rt.com/news/371006-unkraine-reaction-russian-ambassador/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ukrainian MP branded 'TWISTED' after calling Russian ambassador's assassin 'a HERO|url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/world/745540/Ukrainian-MP-called-Russian-ambassador-assassin-Turkey-HERO|publisher=Daily Express|accessdate=2016-12-20|archive-date=2016-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224031557/http://www.express.co.uk/news/world/745540/Ukrainian-MP-called-Russian-ambassador-assassin-Turkey-HERO|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

土耳其方面，总统埃尔多安发布视频短讯，表示“俄土关系对地区关系尤为重要，蓄意破坏者不会得逞。”其后与俄罗斯总统[[弗拉基米尔·普京|弗拉基米尔·普京]]会谈时，他补充道，双方一致同意枪手刺杀俄罗斯驻安卡拉大使是企图伤害两国关系的挑衅行为<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pamuk|first1=Humeyra|last2=Toksabay|first2=Ece|last3=Dolan|first3=David|title=Turkey's Erdogan says Putin agrees shooting of ambassador was provocation|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-russia-diplomat-idUSKBN14829U|website=Reuters|accessdate=2016-12-19|date=2016-12-19|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220210444/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-russia-diplomat-idUSKBN14829U|dead-url=no}}</ref>。外交部承诺不遗余力地阻止袭击事件为俄土关系埋下阴影<ref>{{cite news|title=Turkish MFA says won't allow killing of ambassador 'cast shadow' over Turkish-Russian friendship|url=http://www.dailysabah.com/diplomacy/2016/12/19/turkish-mfa-says-wont-allow-killing-of-ambassador-cast-shadow-over-turkish-russian-friendship|work=DailySabah|accessdate=2016-12-25|archive-date=2019-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190420040152/https://www.dailysabah.com/diplomacy/2016/12/19/turkish-mfa-says-wont-allow-killing-of-ambassador-cast-shadow-over-turkish-russian-friendship|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|土耳其外交部长|List of Ministers of Foreign Affairs (Turkey)|外交部长}}[[梅夫吕特·恰武什奥卢|梅夫吕特·恰武什奥卢]]宣布俄罗斯大使馆所在街道将用大使的名字命名<ref name=221a>{{cite news|title=Turkish police detain six after Russian ambassador shot dead|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-russia-diplomat-idUSKBN1490MK|accessdate=2016-12-20|work=Reuters|date=2016-12-20|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108133305/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-russia-diplomat-idUSKBN1490MK|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

俄罗斯外交部发言人[[玛丽亚·扎哈罗娃|玛丽亚·扎哈罗娃]]表示，恐怖主义不停歇，我们将果断战斗到底<ref name="WP1219">{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/gunfire-wounds-russian-ambassador-in-turkey-reports-say/2016/12/19/ae32d1c8-c608-11e6-85b5-76616a33048d_story.html|title=Russian ambassador to Turkey assassinated in Ankara by off-duty police officer|website=Washington Post|access-date=2016-12-19|archive-date=2017-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107003257/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/gunfire-wounds-russian-ambassador-in-turkey-reports-say/2016/12/19/ae32d1c8-c608-11e6-85b5-76616a33048d_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”普京表示，“已经发生的犯罪行为毫无疑问是一种挑衅，旨在破坏俄土关系正常化和俄罗斯、土耳其、伊朗等国积极推动的叙利亚和平进程”。他要求世界各地的俄罗斯大使馆加强安保，表示需要知道凶手的指挥者<ref name="WP1219" /><ref>{{cite web|last1=Osborn|first1=Andrew|last2=Pomeroy|first2=Robin|title=Putin says ambassador murder is ploy to wreck Syrian peace process|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-russia-diplomat-putin-idUSKBN1482B3|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=2016-12-19|date=2016-12-19|archive-date=2016-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161219233149/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-russia-diplomat-putin-idUSKBN1482B3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[美国国务卿|美国国务卿]][[約翰·福布斯·凱瑞|約翰·福布斯·凱瑞]]表示：“美国谴责今日安卡拉的俄罗斯大使安德烈·卡尔洛夫遇刺事件。我们随时准备向调查此次卑劣且侵犯代表全球各个国家的外交官人身安全权的袭击的俄罗斯和土耳其提供援助<ref>{{cite web|title=Kerry denounces assassination of Russian ambassador|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2016/12/russian-ambassador-killing-john-kerry-reaction-232827|publisher=Politico|accessdate=2016-12-26|date=2016-12-19|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108112931/https://www.politico.com/story/2016/12/russian-ambassador-killing-john-kerry-reaction-232827|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”{{le|美国当选总统|President-elect of the United States}}在社交媒体表示：“今天，我们向被激进伊斯兰教恐怖主义者暗杀的俄罗斯驻土耳其大使安德烈·卡尔洛夫的亲属表示慰问”。“谋杀大使侵犯了一切文明秩序的规则，必须受到一致的谴责<ref>{{cite web|title=Donald Trump Condemns ‘Radical Islamic Terrorist’ Attacks in Berlin, Turkey|url=http://www.breitbart.com/national-security/2016/12/19/donald-trump-condemns-radical-islamic-terrorist-attacks-in-berlin-turkey/|publisher=Breitbart|accessdate=2016-12-26|date=2016-12-19|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108123346/https://www.breitbart.com/national-security/2016/12/19/donald-trump-condemns-radical-islamic-terrorist-attacks-in-berlin-turkey/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

